{
  "version": "28题简版",
  "description": "快速了解你的性格类型，适合初次体验",
  "questions": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "text": "团建晚宴散场后，你第一反应是想赶紧回家窝沙发上回血，还是拉几个人再去喝一杯",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "social",
      "illustration": "sofa.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "搬进新小区第一周，你已经和邻居们聊熟了，还加了几个人的微信",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "social",
      "illustration": "house.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "连续开了一下午的会，你最想做的不是和同事复盘，而是戴上耳机一个人静静待着",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "stress",
      "illustration": "headphones",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "一个人出差时，你会主动约当地的朋友吃顿饭，顺便逛逛这座城市",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "airplane",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "遇到复杂问题时，你习惯先自己想清楚再来找人讨论，而不是边聊边理清思路",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "work",
      "illustration": "lightbulb.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "被困在家里一整天没出门，你会觉得浑身发闷，恨不得马上出去见见人",
