      "direction": "right",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "figure.walk",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "text": "收到一条好消息时，你更想在心里默默感受一下，而不是立刻告诉所有人",
