      "direction": "left",
      "category": "communication",
      "illustration": "heart.text.square.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "text": "逛博物馆时，你会仔细读每件展品的说明文字，而不只是走马观花拍几张照",
