      "direction": "left",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "building.columns.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "text": "看到一个旧物的瞬间，你脑中突然冒出它背后的故事和无数种可能的用途",
