      "category": "learning",
      "illustration": "wand.and.stars.inverse",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "text": "修家电时，你更愿意按说明书一步步排查故障，而不是凭直觉乱拧一通",
