      "direction": "left",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "fork.knife",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "text": "和朋友聊起一部刚看完的电影，你更想讨论导演想表达的深层隐喻",
