      "direction": "right",
      "category": "communication",
      "illustration": "film.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "text": "到新公司上班第一天，你会先搞清楚报销流程和空调遥控器在哪",
