      "direction": "right",
      "category": "work",
      "illustration": "exclamationmark.triangle.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "text": "看到朋友发了一条伤感的动态，你会先放下手头的事去关心对方的情况",
