      "direction": "left",
      "category": "social",
      "illustration": "hand.raised.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "text": "选餐厅时你会先分析评分、人均和评价关键词，而不是凭感觉不错就进去",
