      "direction": "right",
      "category": "decision",
      "illustration": "magnifyingglass",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "text": "小组讨论时如果有人被冷落了，你会主动把话头递给对方，让对方参与进来",
