      "direction": "left",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "theatermasks.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "text": "面对两份工作offer，你会用表格逐条对比薪资、发展、通勤等条件再做决定",
      "dimension": "TF",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "decision",
      "illustration": "tablecells.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "text": "收到周末活动的邀请，你会先确认具体时间地点和流程再决定去不去",
      "dimension": "JP",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "planning",
      "illustration": "calendar",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "text": "出门旅行你更爱走到哪算哪，发现有趣的小巷就拐进去看看，走错路也不慌",
      "dimension": "JP",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "map.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "text": "你的桌面永远只放正在用的东西，文件按颜色标签分得清清楚楚",
