      "direction": "right",
      "category": "work",
      "illustration": "folder.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "text": "Deadline前一天晚上灵感突然爆发，你反而觉得这种状态效率最高",
      "dimension": "JP",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "work",
      "illustration": "bolt.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "text": "每年年初你都会给自己列一整年的目标清单，然后定期回顾进度",
      "dimension": "JP",
      "direction": "right",
