      "illustration": "list.bullet.rectangle.portrait",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "text": "逛街时你更享受漫无目的的闲逛，看到什么有趣就试试，不提前列购物清单",
      "dimension": "JP",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "bag.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "text": "接到一个新项目，你会先拆解出每个阶段的里程碑节点再开始动手",
      "dimension": "JP",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "planning",
      "illustration": "flag.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
